{"tid":60170,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"鳥山明：女兒因《銀魂》惡搞才看我的《龍珠》","createTime":"2016-12-30T08:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T18:20:40.000Z","uid":41343,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bbbb7311642196c0fe220062ec4a4eb2b1eb623f","tid":60170,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:42:58.000Z","msg":"說到日本少年漫畫界的至尊級人物，鳥山明絕對能夠當得起一切榮譽。而他創作的《七龍珠》基本上也是每一個動漫迷都曾經看過、或者至少也是聽說過的吧？<br />\n<br />\n不過近日，老爺子卻在寫感言的時候感謝《銀魂》，理由居然是&ldquo;這部作品讓我的女兒去看《七龍珠》了&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n從網友提供的圖片上可以看到，鳥山明表示：&ldquo;我的女兒是《銀魂》的超級粉絲。買了一大堆周邊之類的東西。而說到她父親的漫畫則根本沒有興趣，她只喜歡不斷地看《銀魂》。有一次，我發現她罕見地拿著《七龍珠》在看，還以爲怎麽了呢，結果她表示只是想看看《銀魂》裏面NETA的原出處而已。空知老師，謝謝你了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n而對此，空知英秋也在下面的評論當中表示：&ldquo;鳥山明老師，不，應該說您的女兒&hellip;&hellip;亦或者稱呼她爲公主？總之真的謝謝了"},{"pid":"ac735be0b67a2e78ee86b4c23e83b47011dd3458","tid":60170,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:46:13.000Z","msg":"gintama"},{"pid":"7c2ff954014d8893f495d3b11395dac404450d10","tid":60170,"uid":9382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:47:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48a26b3b087346a6b112a969acc33bac5ac160c","tid":60170,"uid":46858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:51:38.000Z","msg":"銀他媽！"},{"pid":"abe6ddb1245d79e3a7a333f130e324ae31a76bad","tid":60170,"uid":3976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25240d2692c8d28590b2ce6f9876ac1cc80607c9","tid":60170,"uid":55045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:57:32.000Z","msg":"結果她表示只是想看看《銀魂》裏面NETA的原出處而已。空知老師，謝謝你了。&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7614c9c529d0683e0c8cbac037df89bccd4978","tid":60170,"uid":36432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T18:20:40.000Z","msg":"終於唔洗送禮盒賠罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}